text: Small but well-stocked place with friendly staff. In particular would like to applaud Ms Nurbidayati , a long-time staff and cashier at this outlet. She is always friendly and patient, and goes the extra mile to dispense freebies if we are entitled to them. We would even deliberately wait for her until she is available to check out. 2 story 24 hours supermarket with almost everything you need, although quality wise it's a little lower than the one nearby at bedok mall.

They import in tesco products and all which is amazing and makes me so happy! Excellent staff and self service check out makes everything a breeze!

Great place to be at always!

If you are near tanah merah MRT, this is the nearest fareprice. the other large grocery store would be the giant which is a bit far but a very large store when compared to this faireprice. I perferr to come here as there are many other mini supermarkets, a wet market, fruit shops, vegetable shops and multiple  hawkers are around. this faireprice is small but you can find majority if the groceries here. can get crowdy though.
Small little place can get crowded as the population there is quite large. A little cramp and does not stock certain items. The staff however are great and helpful. 4D outlet is well patronised.
Good gas pump, friendly staff, and I love the polar puffs, nice hot cocoa. There are all normal stuffs for your convenience.
